Description: LIVING ROOM / PRODUCER| Larry Bensky : RECORDED| May 15, 1997. - CONTENT: Hosted by Larry Bensky. Program looks at the CIA/ crack cocaine connection and the articles authored by Gary Webb in the San Jose Mercury News. Guests include author of the series of articles, Gary Webb| Bob Parry, Investigative Reporter and Maxine Waters, Congresswoman. - BROADCAST: May 15, 1997. RESTRICTIONS: None.
